---
title: HelloHero: Herbed Lamb & Cheesy Roast Veg Salad with Garlic Yoghurt
description: No need to be shy, we both know you want to dig in as soon as this meal hits the table. Those juicy roasted lamb slices are oh-so alluring and the call of a bright roast veggie salad is hard to pass up. We say, don’t resist - follow your nose and take a bite! You won’t believe that you made this in no time at all.
